      "content": "but i'm telling you it's not a conspiracy theory to me, i'm actually experiencing it right now. it's like a heavy pressure in my ears and then this sudden spike of anxiety that i can't explain. also i noticed they haven't even been outside today, but the humming is even stronger. it's like it's coming from the walls or something. if someone actually had a directional infrasound emitter, how would they even hide it so it doesn't look obvious to everyone else?",
